### `/dashboard` â€” ðŸ“Š Campaign Highlights

#### Purpose:
Display real-time metrics for the campaign, synced from the Meta Ads API proxy.

#### Components:
- `CampaignMetricsCard` â€“ Display individual KPIs (spend, CTR, clicks, reach, impressions, etc.)
- `LastSynced` â€“ Show last time data was fetched
- `SyncButton` â€“ Manual refresh with automatic rule execution
- **Auto-Sync** â€“ Automatically syncs data when entering dashboard (once per session)

#### Data Source:
- `GET /api/campaigns` â†’ pulls from DB
- `POST /api/sync` â†’ updates from API + triggers rule evaluation

---

### `/automation` â€” âš™ï¸ Rules Manager

#### Purpose:
Create and manage complex automation rules with AND/OR logic that trigger mock actions.

#### Components:
- `RuleBuilder` â€“ Revealbot-style rule creation with condition groups
- `AutomationRulesList` â€“ Table of rules with complex condition display
- `RuleTesting` â€“ Test rules with mock campaign data
- `ActionLogsList` â€“ List of all triggered mock actions

#### Data Source:
- `GET /api/rules` â†’ with condition groups and conditions
- `POST /api/rules` â†’ create complex rules
